  "description": "Welcome to AdvancedBounty, the ultimate bounty hunting plugin for your PocketMine-MP server. Elevate your gameplay by adding thrilling bounty hunting mechanics that allow player...",
  "readme_markdown": "<h2><a id=\"user-content-overview\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#overview\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Overview</h2>\n<p>Welcome to AdvancedBounty, the ultimate bounty hunting plugin for your PocketMine-MP server. Elevate your gameplay by adding thrilling bounty hunting mechanics that allow players to place and claim bounties on others. This feature-rich plugin enhances the excitement on your server and keeps players engaged.</p>\n<p><em>Note: This plugin currently uses JSON to store and modify data.</em></p>\n<h2><a id=\"user-content-features\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#features\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Features</h2>\n<h3><a id=\"user-content-bounty-placement\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#bounty-placement\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Bounty Placement</h3>\n<p>Use the intuitive <code>/bounty</code> command to view all the available commands. Set the reward amount, and watch as the hunt begins. Will your target survive, or will someone claim the bounty?</p>\n<h3><a id=\"user-content-bounty-collection\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#bounty-collection\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Bounty Collection</h3>\n<p>Players with bounties on their heads become the target. Will you be the one to claim the reward by defeating them? AdvancedBounty encourages player interaction and competition.</p>\n<h3><a id=\"user-content-customization\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#customization\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Customization</h3>\n<p>Tailor the plugin to fit your server's unique style. Adjust bounty rewards, reward tax, and more in the easy-to-edit configuration files. Make the plugin work for you!</p>\n<h2><a id=\"user-content-icon\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#icon\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Icon</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.freepik.com/icon/wanted_827170#fromView=search&amp;term=bounty&amp;page=1&amp;position=19\" rel=\"nofollow\">Icon by Freepik</a></p>",
